 \"And his triumph was seemingly made possible by team-mate Sam Dickinson, who appeared to deliberately push the pace on the bike before retiring.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1292, \"end\": 1305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Dickinson\", \"score\": 0.999985295493271, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Dickinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Dickinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Dickinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his triumph\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"the pace\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Discovery+is\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"the new home\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6635207107842033e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The streamer\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"3,800 hours\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1570, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9997244036044157, \"rank\": 0.000275672344954