46, \"to\": 1961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With about 2km to go I thought I'd give it everything I had and I am just so proud that I was able to do that for my family, for everyone that's worked hard, for my girlfriend Liv.\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about 2km\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"my girlfriend Liv\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is so many more people than just me who have worked towards this.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many more people\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was our dream and I am the lucky one who gets to do it, so thank you to them.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our dream\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2236}, {\"ngram\": \"the lucky one\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Show your colours and get Team GB's official kit for the Paris Olympics Do not miss:Team GB snatch second gold in minutes with photo finish in quad sculls rowing Do not miss:Rafael Nadal hits out at 'totally unnecessary' Olympics rule We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2340, \"end\": 2347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999880033102, \"rank\": 1.1996376742027477e-08, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2490, \"end\": 2502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\"